<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l9">in <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> <expan>beyeınand<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeyn <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l10">mıt fleıſſe . Ob Jr ıcht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemet</expan> oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> möchtet . VVas Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l11">gewerb vnd handel da <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / oder wıe ſıe abſchıeden . daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l12">in guter <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet als </ab>
