</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir haben <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        wie daz etwievil <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> der <expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>beyeinand<ex>er</ex></expan> seyn; <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleisse, ob ir icht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemet</expan> oder
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> möchtet, was ir gewerb und handel da
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> oder wie sie abschieden, daz ir uns in
                        guter <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey disem
                            <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, als vil ewch füklich sey und
                        uns zu schreiben gebüre. Als etc. Das wellen etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
